  "2026-04-26T09:56:45.340Z",codex-agent,"Duplicate-check evidence: pm context --limit 10; pm search 'Decision item type missing' --limit 10; pm search 'built-in Decision item type' --limit 10; pm list-open --limit 20; pm list-in-progress --limit 20. Net-new because no open item currently tracks alignment between default type registry/contracts and decision-tracking guidance."
  "2026-04-26T09:57:31.949Z",codex-agent,"Governance evidence: contracts output for create runtime_schema types currently lists Chore,Epic,Event,Feature,Issue,Meeting,Milestone,Reminder,Task with no Decision type, while repository operating guidance expects decision artifacts. Aligning defaults or bootstrap guidance avoids first-run mismatch for agent workflows."
  "2026-04-26T13:16:31.767Z",cursor-agent,"Fresh extension audit evidence 2026-04-26: a temp extension with schema capability successfully registered a custom Decision type and created a Decision item, confirming extensibility works. Default runtime contracts still list only Chore/Epic/Event/Feature/Issue/Meeting/Milestone/Reminder/Task, so first-run Decision guidance remains unresolved."
  "2026-04-26T14:26:04.597Z",cursor-agent,"Implemented Decision as a built-in item type. Changes: added Decision to BUILTIN_ITEM_TYPE_VALUES in src/types.ts, added Decision->decisions mapping in TYPE_TO_FOLDER in src/core/shared/constants.ts, added decisions to PM_OPTIONAL_TYPE_SUBDIRS. Updated tests: shared-constants-errors.spec.ts, completion-command.spec.ts, stats-command.spec.ts. Evidence: pnpm build passed, all 1052 tests pass across 78 files."
